name: Desert Gatherer Droid
description:
Series: Postals from Karaikuera

The Desert Gatherer Droids are mysterious cybercreatures.
These are usually old KOIPO2022 models with machine learning bugged by some kind of malware
They live in lonely hovels along the desert.
Little is known about them except for their scavenger habit of stealing pieces of dead droids that were lucky enough to break down on their lands due to overhitting circuits
Sometimes they lay traps for unprepared travelers from other lands.
The purpose of the stolen pieces is to extend their lives even if they are marginalized from the system.
